word_mean_info__list.difference: 着重独特的程序或方式，尤指个人的偏爱或习惯。
指为达到某种目的或目标而采用的方法、手段或途径。
指从事某事的特别方法、途径。
普通用词，可指一般的方法，有时也指个人的方法或方式，也可指特殊的方式或方法。
指有系统、有条理地办事或解决问题的方法。
多指行动的特殊方式或独特的方法。
书面用词，常指因个人爱好或传统习俗等因素而遵循的方法。

bilingual.target: 他没有任何不正当的手段。

bilingual.source: He used every means to achieve his goal.
bilingual.target: 他用尽各种手段来达到目的。

bilingual.source: Education is a means to improve one's life.
bilingual.target: 教育是一种改善生活的手段。

bilingual.source: They solved the problem through legal means.
bilingual.target: 他们通过合法的手段解决了问题。

bilingual.source: The cheater used unfair means in the exam.
bilingual.target: 作弊者在考试中使用了不正当手段。

bilingual.source: Education is an important means to change one's destiny.
bilingual.target: 教育是改变命运的重要手段。

bilingual.source: He earned a lot of black money through illegal means.
bilingual.target: 他通过非法手段赚取了很多黑金。

bilingual.source: They hope to unify the country through peaceful means.
bilingual.target: 他们希望通过和平手段一统国家。

bilingual.source: They obtained the property through lawful means.
bilingual.target: 他们通过合法的手段获得了这处财产。

bilingual.source: Communication is an essential means of building relationships.
bilingual.target: 沟通是建立关系的重要手段。

list.abstract: means（英[miːnz]，美[miːnz]），英语单词，作前缀为手段；方法。作复数名词为金钱；收入；办法。作动词为表示…的意思；意思是；本意是。短语搭配有by no means（根本不）。例句为“Plastic straws are by no means the biggest source of plastic pollution.（塑料秸秆绝不是塑料污染的最大来源。）” 相关名词近义词有ways、methods，动词近义词有purposes等。

yingyinNormal.en: We use Space Corp, among others, as a means of finding people who are special.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们利用太空公司等多种手段寻找特殊的人才。

yingyinNormal.en: We can finally do something. We have the means to act. Some teenage, pimple-faced hacker.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们总算可以做点什么了，终于有手段了。哪个毛都没长全的少年黑客？

yingyinNormal.en: Refuges or troops of soldiers. Weapons, maybe bombs. A means of an instant strike, that's its military function, isn't it?
yingyinNormal.zh: 难民或者军队，武器或者炮弹，一种瞬间袭击的手段，这就是它的军事功能，对吗？

yingyinNormal.en: All right, we have 48 hours. I have to work Colorado and shore up Tennessee. But Maine, Wisconsin and New hampshire must be turned by any means necessary.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，我们有48小时。我得攻下科罗拉多，稳住田纳西。哪怕采取一切必要手段，也要让缅因，威斯康星和新罕布什尔回心转意。

yingyinNormal.en: Whatever that means. I don't think it means much.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那有什么意义吗？也没多大意义。

yingyinNormal.en: It means a lot, Cory.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这可非同一般，科利。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't know what this means.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我根本不懂这是什么意思。

yingyinNormal.en: No. That means nothing to me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，那对我没有意义。

yingyinNormal.en: That just means it's working.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这只表示收到了效果。

yingyinNormal.en: I have no idea what that means.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我完全不懂你说的是什么。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Night at the Museum: Secret of the Tomb》

yingyinNormal.en: She doesn't know what that means.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她没明白那是什么意思。

yingyinNormal.en: It means you treated me like a dog.
yingyinNormal.zh: 意思是你把我当狗一样。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, if it means that much to you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果你真的觉得很重要。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, I don't know what that means.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不知道那是什么意思。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, and by someone, she means Joey.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对，至于“那个人”，她指的是乔伊。

yingyinNormal.en: So that means I lose, right? It's over!
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以意味着我输了，不是吗? 结束啦!

yingyinNormal.en: And how is it you have means to travel?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你怎么有钱旅行?

yingyinNormal.en: That means you guys would have to stay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可是这样的话，你们也得留下。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Night at the Museum: Secret of the Tomb》

yingyinNormal.en: We don't know what that means. So yeah.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们看不懂那是啥意思，所以，你懂的。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I don't know exactly what it means.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我也不懂那是什么意思。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets》

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: a method or way of doing something

examination_example.sentence: Cattle rearing has been a major <highlight>means</highlight> of livelihood for the poor.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 养牛一直是穷人的主要谋生手段。

examination_example.sentence: Electronic <highlight>means</highlight> of payment may be more efficient than a payments system based on paper.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 电子支付方式可能比基于纸张的支付系统更有效。

examination_example.sentence: A further concern is that the use of electronic <highlight>means</highlight> of payment leaves an electronic trail.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 另一个令人关切的问题是，使用电子支付方式会留下电子痕迹。

word_usage.usage:
means作“方法; 工具; 手段”讲时，单复数同形，如：
a means of storing power 储存能量的办法

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

sense_info_list.en: a method or way of doing something

examination_example.sentence: They prove to be a good <highlight>means</highlight> for managers to give instructions.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 事实证明，它们是管理者给出指示的好方法。

examination_example.sentence: He deplored that broadcasting had become a one-way <highlight>means</highlight> of communication and foresaw it moving in another direction, toward communication as a <highlight>means</highlight> of exchange.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他对广播已经成为一种单向的交流方式表示遗憾，并预见到广播将朝着另一个方向发展，成为一种交流方式。

examination_example.sentence: Car use is in decline as more people move to city centers, while young people especially are opting for other <highlight>means</highlight> of travel.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 随着越来越多的人搬到城市中心，汽车使用量正在下降，而年轻人尤其倾向于选择其他出行方式。

examination_example.sentence: The Grand Tourist was typically a young man with a thorough grounding in Greek and Latin literature as well as some <highlight>means</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: “大游客”(Grand Tourist)通常是年轻人，有扎实的希腊和拉丁文学方面的基础，并且有一些钱。
